! STEOM-CCSD STO-3G TightSCF
# TRIPLET STEOM to isolate the g_phph block (triplet uses g_phph only, no g_phhp).
# Same geometry/basis/frozen=2/complete-active as the singlet run.
# Compare ORCA triplet excitation energies to the Python g_phph-only formula.
%mdci
  nroots 20
  DoSTEOM true
  DoTriplet true
  DoCISNat false
  NActIP 6
  NActEA 4
end
* xyz 0 1
O    0.000000000000     0.000000000000     0.683000000000
C    0.000000000000     0.000000000000    -0.534000000000
H    0.000000000000     0.926000000000    -1.129000000000
H    0.000000000000    -0.926000000000    -1.129000000000
